      <p class="kicker">Privacy and personal control</p><h1 class="page-title">Your private records belong to you.</h1><p class="page-lede">Yoni stores check-ins, journal entries, chat history, and preferences locally in this browser. It does not publish them or turn them into community posts.</p><article class="privacy-summary card"><div><span>Saved check-ins</span><strong id="privacyCheckins">0</strong></div><div><span>Journal entries</span><strong id="privacyJournals">0</strong></div><div><span>Storage</span><strong>This device</strong></div></article><article class="privacy-card card"><h2>Export your records</h2><p>Download a copy of your local check-ins, journal entries, chat, profile, and reminder preference as a JSON file.</p><button class="button orange" id="exportRecords" type="button">Export personal records</button></article><article class="privacy-card card"><h2>Gentle reminder preference</h2><p>Your choice is saved locally. Scheduled notifications are not active yet.</p><label class="preference-field"><span>Reminder setting</span><select id="reminderPreference"><option value="off">Off</option><option value="morning">Gentle morning reminder</option><option value="evening">Gentle evening reminder</option></select></label></article><article class="privacy-card card"><h2>Delete local records</h2><p>Deletion affects only this browser on this device and cannot be undone.</p><div class="privacy-actions"><button class="button soft" id="deleteCheckins" type="button">Delete check-in history</button><button class="button soft" id="deleteJournals" type="button">Delete all journal entries</button><button class="button danger" id="deleteAll" type="button">Delete all local Yoni data</button></div></article>
    </section>

    <section class="screen" id="screen-help" data-screen="help">
      <span id="supportYoni"></span><p class="kicker">Reach a real person</p><h1 class="page-title">Human help comes first.</h1><p class="page-lede">Yoni is a digital companion for reflection and general support. He is not an emergency, medical, psychological, legal, or crisis-response service.</p><div class="hotline-list"><a class="hotline urgent" href="tel:911"><small>Immediate danger or emergency</small><h2>911</h2><p>For police, fire, ambulance, violence, or an immediate threat to safety.</p></a><a class="hotline" href="tel:1553"><small>National Center for Mental Health</small><h2>1553</h2><p>Nationwide NCMH crisis hotline.</p></a><a class="hotline" href="tel:09178998727"><small>NCMH mobile line</small><h2>0917 899 8727</h2><p>Tap to call from a mobile phone.</p></a><a class="hotline" href="tel:09663514518"><small>NCMH mobile line</small><h2>0966 351 4518</h2><p>Tap to call from a mobile phone.</p></a><a class="hotline" href="tel:09086392672"><small>NCMH mobile line</small><h2>0908 639 2672</h2><p>Smart, Sun, and TNT subscribers.</p></a><a class="hotline" href="https://loveyourself.ph/mental-health/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><small>Inclusive community support</small><h2>LoveYourself</h2><p>Mental-health and affirming community support, including LGBTQIA+ focused services.</p></a></div><p class="disclaimer">Hotline availability and phone routing can change. When a number does not connect and there is immediate danger, call 911, contact a trusted person nearby, or go to the nearest emergency department.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="app-footer"><p><strong>Yoni</strong> is a digital companion, not a therapist, doctor, or emergency service.</p></footer>
</div>

